translate chinese mrsmcgee9b_35b65fa8:

    # "For a moment, I think he's going to try to fight me or something because I've been messing around with his wife."
    "那一瞬间，我以为他要跟我打起来，毕竟我一直在调戏他老婆。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mcgee9.rpy:20
translate chinese mrsmcgee9b_0d3bc9f9:

    # "But he doesn't seem upset. If anything, he seems happy."
    "但他似乎并不生气。如果非要说的话，他看起来还挺开心的。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mcgee9.rpy:21
